There is information under the heading Circumstances, including the fact that the item must have been found prior to 1937, but I can't enter that as date of discovery.
Under "Description" it includes sections for Dimensions, Typology, Manufacture, Condition, Surface, Attached Material. 
I have tried to put the Dimensions info into the Length, Width, Edge and Thickness fields. However, several values were quoted for some of the dimensions e.g. Width. I assumed B stood for Breadth i.e. Thickness. I have no idea what DS stands for so I put that value into the Edge field.
I have put the Surface comments into the Surface field.
